# ─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────
#  Invest Market — environment variables
# ─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────
# All data sources have a working fallback, so the app runs with
# ZERO configuration. Add keys below to upgrade specific feeds to
# fully live data.

# Crypto prices & charts use CoinGecko's free public API (no key
# required). Add a Demo/Pro key here only if you hit rate limits.
# COINGECKO_API_KEY=

# Stock & ETF quotes: get a free key at https://finnhub.io
# Without it, the platform serves a realistic live-simulated feed.
# FINNHUB_API_KEY=
